          "explanation": "<div class=\"qml-explanation\"><div class=\"qml-seg\" seg-name=\"详解\">【详解】<p style=\"text-align:justify;word-break:break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">根据电阻定义式</span><math latex=\"$\\mathrm{R}=\\rho \\frac{\\mathrm{L}}{\\mathrm{S}}$\"><mrow><mtext>R</mtext><mo>=</mo><mi>ρ</mi><mfrac><mtext>L</mtext><mtext>S</mtext></mfrac></mrow></math><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，可得电阻的大小与导体的长度成正比，与横截面积成反比。</span></p></div></div>",
